#: ../../source/installation.rst:2
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:7
msgid "Installing the extension"
msgstr "安装插件"

#: ../../source/installation.rst
msgid "Do not unzip the downloaded files!"
msgstr "请勿解压下载的文件！"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:11
msgid "In Blender, click :menuselection:`Edit --> Preferences --> Add-ons`."
msgstr ""
"在 Blender 中，点击 :menuselection:`编辑 --> 首选项 --> 插件`。"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:12
msgid ""
"Click the down arrow in the top-right corner and choose "
":menuselection:`--> Install from Disk...`"
msgstr "点击右上角的下拉箭头按钮，然后选择 :menuselection:`从磁盘安装...`。"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:20
msgid "Remove the extension"
msgstr "卸载插件"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:22
msgid "If the add-on does not provide an **Uninstall** button:"
msgstr "如果插件没有提供 **Uninstall（卸载）** 按钮："

#: ../../source/installation.rst:24
msgid ""
"Open `Blender` and go to :menuselection:`Edit --> Preferences --> Add-"
"ons`."
msgstr ""
"打开 `Blender`，进入 :menuselection:`编辑 --> 首选项 --> 插件`。"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:25
msgid "Locate **Bone Physics** in the list and uncheck it to disable the add-on."
msgstr "在列表中找到 **Bone Physics**，取消勾选以禁用该插件。"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:26
msgid "Manually delete the add-on folder from your `Blender` extension directory."
msgstr "在 `Blender` 的插件目录中手动删除该插件文件夹。"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:27
msgid "Restart `Blender`"
msgstr "重新启动 `Blender`。"

#: ../../source/installation.rst
msgid "The default extension directory is usually located at:"
msgstr "默认的插件目录通常位于："

#: ../../source/installation.rst:32
msgid ""
"`MacOS`: ``~/Library/Application "
"Support/Blender/4.2/extensions/user_default/``"
msgstr ""
"`MacOS`：``~/Library/Application "
"Support/Blender/4.2/extensions/user_default/``"

#: ../../source/installation.rst:33
msgid "`Windows`:"
msgstr "`Windows`："

#: ../../source/installation.rst:34
msgid "`Linux`:"
msgstr "`Linux`："

#: ../../source/installation.rst:36
msgid ""
"The exact path may vary depending on your `Blender` configuration. You "
"should not rely entirely on these paths, check the `File` path instead."
msgstr "具体路径可能会因 `Blender` 配置不同而有所变化。建议在 `File` 路径中查看实际的插件目录。"

